## Setup

Example home configuration:

```nix
# home.nix
{
  programs.jetbra = {
    enable = true;
    enableBashIntegration = true;
    enableZshIntegration = true;
  };

  home.packages = [
    # install your ide packages of choice here
  ];
}
```

You will need to restart your session before launching any installed programs.
